name: I Need It Now

{"name": "I Need It Now  1/22", "description": "

On 2/22/2022 we teamed up to create a record for Web3 and I Need It Now was birthed. The Numerology for 2 is often associated with heightened intuition and sensitivity, as well as the strength and power that comes from connection and collaboration. This was timely because after years of friendship we finally got our chance to align & create in one of our favorite places, Jamaica. We made space to intentionally create without pressure and the process was pure bliss. We allowed spirit to guide us as we produced, wrote and recorded and the smiles never ceased. 

"I Need it Now" is an Affirmative Anthem that encourages listeners to assert and reclaim their worth. Web3 reminds us daily of the power that artists hold individually and collectively, and this song illustrates that in a fun way. We hope that this record gives listeners the confidence to use their voice and stand in their power.

We're offering 22 NFT editions to be collected by our growing community of supporters and we hope you feel the love every time you listen.
